@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_sbjuss(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = (0.40 - 0.92)
    tmp = (((v1 + 0.15 * v0 + 0.63) * v2) * wp.sin((v1 + 0.50 * tmp + 0.64)))
    v2 = wp.cos(wp.exp(wp.abs(v1 + 1.00)))
    v0 = tmp
    v0 = 0.13
    v1 = 0.09
    data[tid] = v0
